# apis/paios/config.http

### Create a new config item

POST https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "key": "openapi-key",
    "value": "abc123"
}

###

### Get all config items with filters

GET https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config?filter={"key":"openapi-key"}
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}

###

### Get a config item by key

GET https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config/openapi-key
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}

###

### Get a specific version of a config item

GET https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config/openapi-key?version=1&environment_id=env-123&user_id=user-123
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}

###

### Update a config item

PUT https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config/openapi-key
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "new-value",
    "environment_id": "env-123",
    "user_id": "user-123"
}

###

### Delete a config item

DELETE https://localhost:8443/api/v1/config/openapi-key?version=1&environment_id=env-123&user_id=user-123
Authorization: Bearer {{PAIOS_BEARER_TOKEN}}
